{"tid":1974430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國武漢肺炎》新加坡新增447宗病例 再創單日新高","createTime":"2020-04-15T23:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T23:16:14.000Z","uid":35519,"like":237,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9bc8fe6a8853fec91a65d44fb5d070155fc83b","tid":1974430,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:34:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新加坡新增447宗病例<br />\n再創單日新高</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新加坡本地今天（15日）新增447宗2019中國武漢肺炎確診病例，再創單日最高紀錄，使累計<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">病例達到3699宗</span></ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n根據衛生部文告，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">新病例都是本地感染病例</span></ins></strong>，並沒有輸入型病例。<br />\n<br />\n其中404宗是住在客工宿舍的工作准證持有者、五人是沒有住宿舍的工作准證持有者，另有38人屬於本地社區感染病例。"},{"pid":"9e92adb41c08616ee586cd4cc0fbd84cbdba3c8f","tid":1974430,"uid":204533,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:37:30.000Z","msg":"你還有(中國共產)黨啊"},{"pid":"3f087afd840b59be62fb82fff11a5ef87fb914ca","tid":1974430,"uid":170249,"like":16,"dislike":29,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:38:30.000Z","msg":"坡狗nmsl"},{"pid":"40dd61390ded2acbddd7fc94c098407e9299e923","tid":1974430,"uid":25794,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:39:42.000Z","msg":"Monkey奶野鳥"},{"pid":"988d656945c3a9ab677365ef41c0653541103a13","tid":1974430,"uid":51701,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:40:14.000Z","msg":"新加坡特別行政區政府害死市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ded81a8ec87bed230f9c74bf030f89146c0ec8","tid":1974430,"uid":39365,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:42:10.000Z","msg":"新加坡隔離既馬來西亞都爆得幾勁，分分鍾都係新加坡傳過去既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a434af8a6e4bb70b778b9458f5ec947ccdc8e831","tid":1974430,"uid":152222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T23:42:23.00